translate

public Substitution translate(Substitution phantoms)
Transform substitution of phantoms to substitution of valid IveObjects. Tranformation of some sources can fails then slot stay empty. Due to this, Substitution.checkSubstitution(Substitution) method should be called after translation.

Returns:
new object of translated substitution
